   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,022:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Tools
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,023:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Go Vocal (formerly CitizenLab) — Brussels, Belgium
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,024:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,025:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What they do:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,035:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  SaaS community engagement platform for local governments. AI-powered analytics
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,038:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (sentiment detection, topic clustering, trend analysis). Used by Cambridge City Council (UK) and
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,039:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: hundreds of EU municipalities.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,040:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Why partner:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Most commercially mature civic participation platform. Strong EU presence;
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: expanding to North America.
