   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,054:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: budgeting. Experimenting with GPT integration. Democratically governed.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,054:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-17 12:39:08,055:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Why partner:
